<p>东风风神AX7 PRO上市，这造型还挺酷</p>
<p>9月10号，东风风神AX7 2021款和东风风神AX7 PRO正式上市，价格为8.99-14.39万元。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200911/382cf2c778da4a3aa217308f5c70e5dd.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200911/8146fb5be2ce4be4bdb8c67d599dc42e.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200911/482a1f4537494512ac9528d214965221.png" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
